properties.title: representative
properties.name: Matthew Cartwright
properties.biography: Matthew Cartwright, a Representative from Pennsylvania; born in Erie, Erie County, Pa., May 1, 1961; A.B., Hamilton College, Clinton, N.Y., 1983; attended Temple University School of Law, Philadelphia, Pa., 1984; J.D., University of Pennsylvania, Philadelphia, Pa., 1986; lawyer, private practice; elected as a Democrat to the One Hundred Thirteenth and to the two succeeding Congresses (January 3, 2013-present).
